I noticed that various resources aren't properly cleaned up in various classes. To be specific,
* Some streams aren't properly cleaned up in {{beeline/src/java/org/apache/hive/beeline/BeeLine.java}} and {{beeline/src/java/org/apache/hive/beeline/BeeLineOpts.java}}
* {{Statement}}, {{ResultSet}}, and {{Connection}} aren't properly cleaned up in {{beeline/src/java/org/apache/hive/beeline/HiveSchemaTool.java}}
* {{Statement}} and {{ResultSet}} aren't properly cleaned up in  {{jdbc/src/java/org/apache/hive/jdbc/HiveConnection.java}}
